June 27 [1938]\x{2014}<<12:00|2>> [Monday]
Now it is Monday. And I took two days off and have a little trouble getting into the swing. For one thing Pat* can\x{2019}t meet royalty payment and is paying one third, with notes for another two thousand. This is all right if it doesn\x{2019}t indicate that he is in difficulty. That worries me a little but not much. Ed came for the weekend. Good Ed.* We ran down to [Ed.\x{2014}Pacific] Grove Saturday night to inject 300 hagfish\x{2014}ugly, slimy brutes, and much better looking full of formaldehyde. That knocked the slime. Ritch and Tal* drove back. They are all coming next Saturday night for the week end of the Fourth. Short story volume [Ed.\x{2014}The Long Valley] comes out in early Sept. It will collapse of course but I\x{2019}ll be glad to have it out. May sell three or four thousand copies. People looking at the next lot. We really must get out of here. I would love so much to go over to the Aptos country [Ed.\x{2014}south of Santa Cruz]. Hear the ocean that I love. But must let Carol decide since she lives so much in her environment. Got a mild muscle [Ed.\x{2014}spasm] in my chest and was dizzy this morning. I don\x{2019}t know why. This place is getting as noisy as a city lot. There is a lot of talk in the diary this morning\x{2014}reason is to relieve the tension and get even with myself. Doesn\x{2019}t matter since I can work later this afternoon. Now for a discussion. Moment I stopped work the drive became sexual. Now the work will take that up. Now today\x{2019}s work is the pig killing and salting and the loading of the truck and the departure and the capture of Grampa  [Ed.\x{2014}last sections of Chapter 10]. That is at least two days or maybe three, and then the next general is the empty house. Take out the last paragraph of the last general for the next. I\x{2019}m a little sick today. I don\x{2019}t know why. I guess that\x{2019}s why I\x{2019}m so talkative this week\x{2014}it is time to go to work and that is all there is to it.",
